div.p:
Interest rates have been increased slightly in the small categories. Up
                            to $10,000, the new rate will be 3½%; between $10,000 and $20,000, 3¼%;
                            between $20,000 and $50,000,3%; between $50,000 and $100,000, 2¾%;
                            between $100,000 and $200,000, 2½%; between $200,000 and $400,000, 2%;
                            between $400,000 and $600,000, 1½%; between $600,000 and $800,000, 1¼%;
                            and above $800,000, 1%.
